headline: American Bitcoin pops on debut, Adidas & Wynn Resorts upgraded
summary: Josh Lipton and Prairie Operating Co. executive vice president of market strategy and TheBigSkinny.com founder Lou Basenese examine what's driving interest in some of the trending tickers during Wednesday's session. The pair discuss American Bitcoin's (ABTC) debut on the Nasdaq Composite (^IXIC), Jefferies analysts' bullish call on Adidas (ADDYY), and Argus upgrading Wynn Resorts (WYNN). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination.
